Okay, The concept is this, there are 3 terrorists and 40 Counter-terrorists. The Cts only have a pistole and a knife, but up to 40 teammates.

The terrorists spawn with a CK47 DuelPistols and a Grenade, Also they have a Buy zone.

The teams are Set loose in the Maze and have to kill each other.

EasterEggs/hiddinStuff: There are Two invisible ladders, and one invisible Platform
